  "text": "In land-based steam power plants produced power is main steam turbine power. If the land-based steam power plant has auxiliary steam turbines, their power is usually much lower than the power produced by main turbine, so the power of auxiliary steam turbines in such steam power plants can be neglected in the equation [CITATION_1] .",
